n自己起一幢當然要承擔返成本啦<br />\n當初唔好叫<span style=\"color: red;\">成功爭取</span>囉"},{"pid":"fe6f98542f245fc8586372d182bcfe32bc3ca39d","tid":966924,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:29:56.000Z","msg":"當初明明話粵劇場館同其他opera 既設計唔同<br />\n連座位擺法, 音響, 設備, 後台唔一樣"},{"pid":"930dd224e764814116261d88fb0ea97608eebbcb","tid":966924,"uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"而家先知？香港豬閪多"},{"pid":"f6241c61978d445ccbf3028fa58dd225da8481dc","tid":966924,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"讓大陸劇團先用"},{"pid":"e0b72c227341a982f0647e0fd8cb9a1933740d54","tid":966924,"uid":16676,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:34:11.000Z","msg":"起好又話要行政獨立, 管理獨立<br />\n要獨立於西九文化局<br />\n行政, 演出, 劇本唔可以比西九其他人干擾<br />\n<br />\n唐英年唔支薪同你做義工<br />\n其他人都唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都唔出糧咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1471597b671516ffe5a9df68c4d75bb6e38f94","tid":966924,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"8758e3dc45d2ca85bb04415ef146cbec1891c6c5","tid":966924,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T07:33:03.000Z","msg":"粵劇中心好似用普通話譯音做名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"我屌鳩你老母家姐細妹同埋你個女<br />\n鳩up都要有個限度 咁樣用&quot;好似&quot;去誤導人好咩<br />\n<br />\n中國無論點柒法 對外都會用Chinese Opera<br />\n下面係其中一個例子<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shchineseoperas.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shchineseoperas.org%2F&d=qaW8S7LnwtA7LVK%2BarviWZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c1fd7404\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.shchineseoperas.org/</a>"},{"pid":"ba124ccfd827dbfdd1855d6b4f24b1831c019cde","tid":966924,"uid":49216,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:38:43.000Z","msg":"成班傻閪宜家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇個名就知唔係比香港人用啦<br />\n成班後知後覺奶共狗<br />\n就算你奶到雪雪聲，利用完你之後都係condom咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地要場未起比你地囉，你租唔起，我先請內地劇團咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786e8e7928bf000256db2b38302d022bda6d208d","tid":966924,"uid":65530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83f4ee2b0ecf25a28cfbdaaed81f1b7a0d764b08","tid":966924,"uid":153418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8758e3dc45d2ca85bb04415ef146cbec1891c6c5","tid":966924,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T07:33:03.000Z","msg":"粵劇中心好似用普通話譯音做名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"私處<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d993c3983aae72bce862638489b8123899cb51c","tid":966924,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"演出場地需專為粵劇而建，場地設計絕對不能只以西方音樂或歌劇作準，<span style=\"color: red;\">故場地用料、座椅物料及分佈、調音板等設備均需考慮粵劇音樂及鑼鼓的特質</span>。另外設立較大型的女洗手間，升降機，停車場等亦是關顧之列。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkbarwo.com/aboutus_goal.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkbarwo.com%2Faboutus_goal.php&d=qaW8S7LnwtA7LVK%2BarviWZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8f416cef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkbarwo.com/aboutus_goal.php</a><br />\n唔係我鳩up, 當日汪阿蛆八和係咁強調<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f776798f31e180008befc54f6ad38023ee945736","tid":966924,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200606/28/P200606280247.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200606%2F28%2FP200606280247.htm&d=qaW8S7LnwtA7LVK%2BarviWZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2fe2e048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200606/28/P200606280247.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n粵劇團體指本港一直對粵劇發展缺乏足夠支援，而政府計劃用作粵劇表演的高山劇場亦非理想的粵劇表演場地。<br />\n<br />\n而家起好就想拎funding <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f38147d7149f98519f2f47f36db6c4c4af453c","tid":966924,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:50:13.000Z","msg":"中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搲維穩基金囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d242d44a55e8b4f9d9062c30c04504c309ae3e2b","tid":966924,"uid":28397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f1471597b671516ffe5a9df68c4d75bb6e38f94","tid":966924,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"8758e3dc45d2ca85bb04415ef146cbec1891c6c5","tid":966924,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T07:33:03.000Z","msg":"粵劇中心好似用普通話譯音做名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"我屌鳩你老母家姐細妹同埋你個女<br />\n鳩up都要有個限度 咁樣用&quot;好似&quot;去誤導人好咩<br />\n<br />\n中國無論點柒法 對外都會用Chinese Opera<br />\n下面係其中一個例子<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shchineseoperas.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shchineseoperas.org%2F&d=qaW8S7LnwtA7LVK%2BarviWZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c1fd7404\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.shchineseoperas.org/</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji