tid":966924,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T07:05:24.000Z","msg":"西九戲曲中心經過5年施工，日前終於落成，將於本月20日開幕。香港粵劇商會主席杜韋秀明今早出席港台節目時表示，戲曲中心場租貴，業界難以負擔。<br />\n<br />\n杜韋秀明指，業界現時多租用政府場地，例如高山劇場、文化中心等，因為有政府資助，業界能接受場租。她舉例，高山劇場全日租金不用8,000元，相比時戲曲中心全日租金接近7萬多元，佔總支出40至50%，兩者費用「分別非常之大」。<br />\n<br />\n杜韋秀明表示，兩年前曾向西九方面反映，如果折扣後的場租只比文化中心貴少許，他們仍能接受。業界亦曾提議按票價定場租，惟當局聆聽後未有表示。當局其後解釋指，因西九是自負盈虧，沒有政府資助，故定價較高，建議先運作，一年後再檢討。她稱，雖然戲曲中心各方面是不錯，但「一計落條數」，即使怎樣「好、靚」，「我哋係負擔唔到嘅時候，即係呢個場地都唔係畀我哋用囉」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/266627/%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%B2%E6%9B%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%97%A5%E7%A7%9F%E8%BF%917%E8%90%AC%E9%9B%A3%E8%B2%A0%E6%93%94%e3%80%80%E7%B2%B5%E5%8A%87%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%A2/?fbclid=IwAR2TLcWTJ1LhayPkYtIDC8cU0h1dsRr-3md0ayf1XUGwqcwFicvG26tRPbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F266627%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%2588%25B2%25E6%259B%25B2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25A7%259F%25E8%25BF%25917%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%259B%25A3%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E6%2593%2594%25e3%2580%2580%25E7%25B2%25B5%25E5%258A%2587%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2591%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2TLcWTJ1LhayPkYtIDC8cU0h1dsRr-3md0ayf1XUGwqcwFicvG26tRPbM&d=qaW8S7LnwtA7LVK%2BarviWZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6eadf1b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/266627/%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%B2%E6%9B%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%97%A5%E7%A7%9F%E8%BF%917%E8%90%AC%E9%9B%A3%E8%B2%A0%E6%93%94%e3%80%80%E7%B2%B5%E5%8A%87%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%A2/?fbclid=IwAR2TLcWTJ1LhayPkYtIDC8cU0h1dsRr-3md0ayf1XUGwqcwFicvG26tRPbM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"超支都要圍本"},{"pid":